[22/07/2018 14:00:25] <font color="#ffffff">Hay grandes similitudes</font>
[22/07/2018 14:00:25] <font color="#ffffff">entre ambos.</font>
[22/07/2018 14:00:27] <font color="#ffff00">¿Y si volviera a ocurrir?</font>
